The summary of the hypotheses testing is shown in Table 5. Self-Efficacy (β = 0.196, p < 0.001), Subjective Norm (β = 0.157, p < 0.05), Enjoyment (β = 0.286, p < 0.001), and Experience (β = 0.421, p = 0.051) positively and significantly associated with students’ PEOU of the e-portfolio, supporting hypotheses 1, 4, 5 and 8.

